This PR adds more fix for #6752.
Besides handle null pointer exception, in this PR I added an action for update chart id in charts reducer. this will make chart reducer and explore reducer state consistent.

@kristw @michellethomas

This adds Apache Rat license checks to the build matrix. 

It sets a count and saves this in the caching directory. The count cannot go up higher otherwise PRs will fail. To move it a little bit faster you could subtract an arbitrary number to force contributors to add extra headers.

@mistercrunch
